{"tid":341464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Splatoon2] 你會選哪種調味料呢？美乃滋 vs 番茄醬","createTime":"2017-07-30T18:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T18:18:20.000Z","uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3492e23c226af321857ad5fdf1a6232b168352","tid":341464,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你會選哪種調味料呢？</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">美乃滋</span> vs <span style=\"color: red;\">番茄醬</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201707/9411e547b1af44c5d8d733c8daf23c10.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201707%2F9411e547b1af44c5d8d733c8daf23c10.JPG&h=308a528e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n在此通知祭典即將舉行的消息。<br />\n題目是「你喜歡哪一種？美乃滋 VS 番茄醬」。<br />\n這次是由兩種活躍於各種料理的調味料所進行的對抗賽。<br />\n如果要在兩者之間選擇其一，你到底會選擇哪種呢？<br />\n活動時間將於 2017 年 8 月 4 日 14:00 ～ 8 月 5 日 14:00 其間舉行。<br />\n<br />\n另外，本次祭典的題目為全球統一。因此即便各地舉辦時間不同，全世界依舊會在這個周末舉辦相同主題的祭典。結果統計方面也會依照日本、北美、澳洲／紐西蘭、歐洲等地個別計算，不過還是會公開各區的統計結果喔，敬請期待。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">正評：美乃滋</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">負評：番茄醬</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"af11522ccd7ce7852a983de6fd8425c1aa6617ed","tid":341464,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:18:08.000Z","msg":"錯台 自膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請去第二個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/341465/page/1?post=58b6e8eea4fc952b11bca24b8593a275a1115700\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/341465/page/1?post=58b6e8eea4fc952b11bca24b8593a275a1115700</a>"},{"pid":"dc7b8c49efc529e7088c94a7a0db6ce8a6e9b4e2","tid":341464,"uid":118995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:18:20.000Z","msg":"屌你兩樣都咁好味好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}